## install python sds sdk
```
git clone https://github.com/XiaoMi/galaxy-sdk-python.git
cd galaxy-sdk-python
python setup.py install
```

## install requirements
```
pip install -r requeirements.txt
```

## Run
```
# MUST RUN IN THIS DIR
DOUBAN_CRAWL_ENV=STAGING python -m douban.douban_scheduler
DOUBAN_CRAWL_ENV=STAGING python -m douban.douban_crawler_consumer
DOUBAN_CRAWL_ENV=STAGING python -m douban.douban_struct_to_convs
# or use nohup
DOUBAN_CRAWL_ENV=C3 nohup python -m douban.douban_crawler_consumer &> /path/to.log&
```